				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%E1%BA%A4t-S%E1%BB%ADu-trung-thu-h%E1%BA%ADu-ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Chi-th%E1%BB%8B-c%E1%BA%A3m-Nh%C6%B0-V%C3%A2n-ca-nhi-t%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BB%9Di-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-Cj5FEJpfXnMIu_jizKYojA">Ất Sửu trung thu hậu hoạ Đông Chi thị cảm Như Vân ca nhi tại thời nguyên vận - 乙丑中秋後和東芝氏感如雲歌兒在辰原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/B%C3%ADnh-T%C3%BD-ni%C3%AAn-ng%C5%A9-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-nh%E1%BA%ADt-du-T%C3%B9ng-lu%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BA%A5n-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-dF6KO44U7DADwHlMyRQSHQ">Bính Tý niên ngũ nguyệt nhị thập ngũ nhật du Tùng luật hải tấn hữu cảm - 丙子年五月二十五日遊從律海汛有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Giang-b%E1%BA%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%99-t%E1%BA%A7m-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-9ydL3-qxJHzztAT6wTAywg">Giang bạn độc bộ tầm hoa kỳ 1 - 江畔獨步尋花其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-xu%C3%A2n/poem-6K2vTzfW55WPuZY9rXePaA">Hoạ đường xuân - 畫堂春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-VcJOg6OMnUKwRFzXmhMIag">Triệu Trường Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/T%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-kUcIb61rXbi3B3d6EXq0xw">Tạ tân ân kỳ 1 - 謝新恩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jH